children.text: My name is Ivana. I'm a software engineer based in New York.

I was born in Germany but grew up in Pennsylvania. After graduating from NYU with a BA in English, I worked briefly in the NYC start-up scene before moving to Berlin, Germany, to teach at a bootcamp there. After 3.5 rewarding years at the bootcamp, I decided to leave my job to pursue other opportunities back in NYC
